        <!--Begin In School Enrollment Questions-->
        <h3 class="btn-About">In School</h3>
        <div id="aboutInSchoolFaq">
            <h4 class="questions">What do I need to do while I'm in school to make sure my loans are in good standing?</h4>
            <div class="answers-aboutInSchool1 answers" id="inSchoolAnswer1">
                If you chose to pay the interest on your unsubsidized loans while you're in school,
